      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the caution part but 2000 or 5000 feels so low if i'm actually deficient. i read some wellness blogs that say loading up with huge doses for a short burst is actually the best way to saturate your cells and fix the deficit way faster. if i only do it for like 14 days, wouldn't my body just process it? i'm pretty healthy so i don't think i'll have issues.",
